{"tid":2105833,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳聞指 Apple 正開發遊戲主機   採用自家 ARM 架構處理器","createTime":"2020-07-13T02:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T20:25:50.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1e95ba2dd43489c8fcf42f2ddb882a1f4c410d30","tid":2105833,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:15:02.000Z","msg":"有細心留意 Apple 近年的產品和服務，可能會發現他們比以往更加重視遊戲市場，例如自從 iOS 13 起，iPhone 和 iPad 都可以輕鬆連接 Xbox One 和 PlayStation 4 遊戲手掣，同樣的安排亦在 Apple TV 上提供。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSCzxNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSCzxNV.jpg&h=19ecd36c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年推出的 Apple Arcade 月費計劃，則是 Apple 正式將遊戲作為服務推出的商品，讓玩家能夠以一個月費玩到大量遊戲，同時毋須額外課金和觀看廣告。最近有小道消息指 Apple 內部正在開發遊戲主機產品，而且會使用自家 ARM 架構的處理器，由於爆料者只透露 Apple 正在開發遊戲主機，未有公開其他細節，所以無法估計是什麼類型的遊戲機。<br />\n<br />\n現時發售中的 Apple TV 就已經支援 Apple Arcade 服務，而 Apple TV 所使用的處理器，自從第二代開始就使用自家 A 系處理器，所以，爆料者指 Apple 正在開發遊戲主機，可能只是 Apple TV 使用更新更高效能的處理器，標榜甚至捆綁 Apple Arcade 服務而已。<br />\n<br />\n來源：cnbeta"},{"pid":"9d5594d8956d8b8729d8b4f2d1c4a2e2c7215546","tid":2105833,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"今年WWDC仲有Bring keyboard and mouse gaming to iPad<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fvideos%2Fplay%2Fwwdc2020%2F10617&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=fa154da5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10617</a><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><br />\nLevel up your iPad games and add in keyboard, mouse, and trackpad controls. Discover how to use the Game Controller framework to augment your existing titles, bring over games from other platforms, or dream up entirely new interaction experiences. Learn how to integrate keyboard and &ldquo;delta&rdquo; mouse coordinate events for player motion, and disable pointer system gestures like the Dock or Control Center to take full advantage of full screen gameplay. For further information on adding support for console game controllers like the Xbox Elite Wireless Controller Series 2 and Xbox Adaptive Controller, watch &ldquo;Advancements in Game Controllers.&rdquo; And learn more about using UIKit to manage indirect input by checking out &ldquo;Handle trackpad and mouse input&rdquo;.</span>"},{"pid":"578027df29cb0336aca071197c7c39606eb58fb7","tid":2105833,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"arm mac上市後，developer用arm+metal api開發一次隻game就可以喺晒iPhone、iPad、Mac、Apple TV上玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次x86+DX12 ult開發一次就可以係Win10同XboxSX都run到<br />\n<br />\n我開發game嘅話一定mark實呢兩個平台先，CP值極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ceffcd6aced25dbe2ef2c038225314e6528096","tid":2105833,"uid":5686,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"578027df29cb0336aca071197c7c39606eb58fb7","tid":2105833,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"arm mac上市後，developer用arm+metal api開發一次隻game就可以喺晒iPhone、iPad、Mac、Apple TV上玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次x86+DX12 ult開發一次就可以係Win10同XboxSX都run到<br />\n<br />\n我開發game嘅話一定mark實呢兩個平台先，CP值極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"最後都只係無限課金/廣告GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7398ab8c10c1df24055838c264d1b4b71814c44a","tid":2105833,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58ceffcd6aced25dbe2ef2c038225314e6528096","tid":2105833,"uid":5686,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"578027df29cb0336aca071197c7c39606eb58fb7","tid":2105833,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTim