<br />\nA14開始可能勁過PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"下？<br />\nSwitch係iPhone 7級數"},{"pid":"5351688e7415a1b42c39fb4e620a2af63f30c224","tid":2105833,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"一萬蚊一部遊戲機不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵撚買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1005124dadda442e4fb59742c5e9ae0600e575b4","tid":2105833,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57fea557c08c9d7e2fb746849a2fb30cccf31c20","tid":2105833,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff1de15d60623a0f1a7d179f3e9dbf353c30660","tid":2105833,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"點解你地會第一時間覺得係手機Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA12Z粒GPU好似同Switch係打和（唔限制Watt數）<br />\n<br />\nA14開始可能勁過PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"下？<br />\nSwitch係iPhone 7級數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"CPU嘅話，大家都係16nm ARMv8-A，應該差唔遠<br />\n<br />\n但GPU，FP32嚟計<br />\nTegra X1有0.649 TFLOPS（Switch特製版應該會再高啲）<br />\nA10 Fusion得0.249 TFLOP<br />\n<br />\nA12Z無資料，但可能已經有0.8 TFLOPS<br />\n其實係勉強玩到3A大作<br />\n所以先會用嚟做ARM Mac OS嘅開發機<br />\n<br />\n不過問題係，就算畀佢A14X去到2.0 TFLOPS都好<br />\nApple應該唔會肯賣咁平<br />\n但人地PS5講緊10.28 TFLOPS可能只係賣3、4千<br />\n策略嚟講動搖唔到M$同SONY"}]}